title: A sermon preached before the Kings Most Excellent Majesty at Oxford by H.K., D.D.
author: Killigrew, Henry, 1613-1700.
notes: Attributed to Henry Killigrew by BM and Halkett & Laing (2nd ed.); also attributed to Henry King.
